'''乔纳斯·纽鲍尔'''（{{lang-en|Jonas Neubauer}}，{{bd|1981年|11月21日|2021年|1月4日|catIdx=Neubauer}}）是美国[[俄羅斯方塊|俄罗斯方块]]玩家，曾在[[經典俄羅斯方塊世界錦標賽|經典俄羅斯方塊世界錦標賽]]七度奪得冠军<ref name="kotaku">{{Cite web|title=16-Year-Old Dethrones Tetris World Champion With Difficult Hyper-Tap Technique|url=https://kotaku.com/16-year-old-dethrones-tetris-world-champion-with-diffic-1829911215|accessdate=2021-01-09|author=Gach|date=2018-10-22|first=Ethan|publisher=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]|archive-date=2022-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220407094312/https://kotaku.com/16-year-old-dethrones-tetris-world-champion-with-diffic-1829911215}}</ref>，他在游戏職業生涯中积极推广这项[[电子竞技|电子竞技]]运动，在俄罗斯方块社群中享有盛誉。他在成为游戏主播前是[[加州|加州]][[托伦斯|托伦斯]]一间酒吧的经理。<ref name="ginx">{{Cite web|title=Jonas Neubauer, 7-time Tetris World Champion, dies age 39|url=https://www.ginx.tv/en/video-games/jonas-neubauer-7-time-tetris-world-champion-dies-at-age-39|accessdate=2021-01-09|author=Sandoval|date=2021-01-09|first=Alejandro|publisher=[[Ginx_TV|Ginx TV]]|archive-date=2022-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220328084807/https://www.ginx.tv/en/video-games/jonas-neubauer-7-time-tetris-world-champion-dies-at-age-39}}</ref><ref name="vice">{{Cite web|title=This Bartender Is Secretly the Greatest Tetris Player in the World|url=https://www.vice.com/en/article/5988gb/this-bartender-is-secretly-the-greatest-tetris-player-in-the-world|accessdate=2021-01-09|author=Neumann|date=2018-10-19|first=Sean|publisher=[[Vice_(magazine)|Vice]]|archive-date=2022-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220209090518/https://www.vice.com/en/article/5988gb/this-bartender-is-secretly-the-greatest-tetris-player-in-the-world}}</ref><ref name="tetris interview">{{Cite web|title=The Life of a Tetris Master - Interview With Jonas Neubauer|url=https://tetris.com/article/121/the-life-of-a-tetris-master-interview-with-jonas-neubauer|accessdate=2021-01-09|author=Shaver|date=2017-10-13|first=Morgan|publisher=[[The_Tetris_Company|The Tetris Company]]|archive-date=2022-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220430033446/https://tetris.com/article/121/the-life-of-a-tetris-master-interview-with-jonas-neubauer}}</ref><ref name="rollingstone">{{Cite web|title=King of the Block: Meet the World’s Greatest ‘Tetris’ Player|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/culture/culture-sports/king-of-the-block-meet-the-worlds-greatest-tetris-player-189599/|accessdate=2021-01-09|author=Ritchie|date=2014-10-16|first=Ryan|publisher=[[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]]|archive-date=2022-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220209085952/https://www.rollingstone.com/culture/culture-sports/king-of-the-block-meet-the-worlds-greatest-tetris-player-189599/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Jonas Neubauer, the Greatest Tetris Player, Is Dead|url=https://heavy.com/games/jonas-neubauer-dead/|accessdate=2021-01-09|author=Fennimore|date=2021-01-09|first=Jack|publisher=[[Heavy_(website)|Heavy]]|archive-date=2021-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211216235642/https://heavy.com/games/jonas-neubauer-dead/}}</ref>。

== 生平 ==
乔纳斯·纽鲍尔6至7岁的时候就开始在叔叔的[[麥金塔|麦金塔电脑]]上玩俄罗斯方块，并从9岁开始玩[[红白机|NES]]版本。<ref name="shacknews">{{Cite web|title=7-time world champion Jonas Neubauer talks the continuing rise of Classic Tetris|url=https://www.shacknews.com/article/114575/7-time-world-champion-jonas-neubauer-talks-the-continuing-rise-of-classic-tetris|accessdate=2021-01-09|author=Mejia|date=2019-10-21|first=Ozzie|publisher=[[Shacknews|Shacknews]]|archive-date=2021-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210506130905/https://www.shacknews.com/article/114575/7-time-world-champion-jonas-neubauer-talks-the-continuing-rise-of-classic-tetris}}</ref>2006年11月，他提供了第一个已知的“maxout”（999,999分）游戏录像 <ref>{{Cite web|title=NES Tetris - 999,999|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qYDPMHkHh8s|accessdate=2021-01-09|date=2006-11-11|publisher=[[YouTube|YouTube]]|archive-date=2021-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210728075102/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qYDPMHkHh8s}}</ref>；2008年9月，他上传了从第19级开始并“maxout”的游戏录像。<ref>{{Cite web|title=NES Tetris Level 19 Maxout 999,999|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TIVyMENph7Y|accessdate=2021-01-09|date=2008-09-04|publisher=[[YouTube|YouTube]]|archive-date=2021-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210728075108/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TIVyMENph7Y}}</ref>

乔纳斯参加了2010年首届经典俄罗斯方块世界锦标赛，并在决赛中击败哈里·洪（Harry Hong）赢得冠军。 <ref name="shacknews">{{Cite web|title=7-time world champion Jonas Neubauer talks the continuing rise of Classic Tetris|url=https://www.shacknews.com/article/114575/7-time-world-champion-jonas-neubauer-talks-the-continuing-rise-of-classic-tetris|accessdate=2021-01-09|author=Mejia|date=2019-10-21|first=Ozzie|publisher=[[Shacknews|Shacknews]]}}</ref>他赢得了接下来三年的比赛，在2014年败给哈里·洪排名第二。2015年至2017年，纽鲍尔赢得了其间三次世界冠军，直到在2018年的决赛中被16岁的约瑟夫·塞勒（Joseph Saelee）击败。 <ref name="kotaku">{{Cite web|title=16-Year-Old Dethrones Tetris World Champion With Difficult Hyper-Tap Technique|url=https://kotaku.com/16-year-old-dethrones-tetris-world-champion-with-diffic-1829911215|accessdate=2021-01-09|author=Gach|date=2018-10-22|first=Ethan|publisher=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]}}</ref>

2018年1月，纽鲍尔在练习清除100行时，以1分57秒意外创下了最快获得30万分的世界纪录。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Random: Twitch Streamer Accidentally Sets New Tetris World Record|url=https://www.nintendolife.com/news/2018/01/random_twitch_streamer_accidentally_sets_new_tetris_world_record|accessdate=2021-01-09|author=Craddock|date=2018-01-04|first=Ryan|publisher=[[NintendoLife|NintendoLife]]|archive-date=2021-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210606154514/https://www.nintendolife.com/news/2018/01/random_twitch_streamer_accidentally_sets_new_tetris_world_record}}</ref>

2018年6月，乔纳斯创造了1,245,200分的（当时）世界最高纪录。 <ref>{{Cite web|title=Boom! [Former] World Record High Score for Jonas! 1,245,200 points|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4hIzK7DgH6M|accessdate=2021-01-09|date=2018-06-22|publisher=[[YouTube|YouTube]]|archive-date=2022-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220330121752/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4hIzK7DgH6M}}</ref>

=== 去世 ===
2021年1月4日，纽鲍尔因突发疾病在夏威夷去世，享年39岁。<ref name="ginx">{{Cite web|title=Jonas Neubauer, 7-time Tetris World Champion, dies age 39|url=https://www.ginx.tv/en/video-games/jonas-neubauer-7-time-tetris-world-champion-dies-at-age-39|accessdate=2021-01-09|author=Sandoval|date=2021-01-09|first=Alejandro|publisher=[[Ginx_TV|Ginx TV]]}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=曾來台的《俄羅斯方塊》世界冠軍 Jonas Neubauer 因突發疾病逝世|url=https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=209051|accessdate=2021-01-17|last=巴哈姆特|work=巴哈姆特電玩資訊站|archive-date=2021-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111114423/https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=209051|dead-url=no}}</ref>
尸检显示其死因是未知原因的[[心脏节律不整|心脏节律不整]]造成的[[心脏停止|心脏停止]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=Jonas Neubauer Twitter|url=https://twitter.com/neubsauce/status/1378124171285127168|url-status=live|access-date=2021-04-03|website=Twitter|language=en|archive-date=2021-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210525072703/https://twitter.com/neubsauce/status/1378124171285127168}}</ref>

== 轶事 ==
西班牙电子竞技评论员{{link-es|Ibai|Ibai_Llanos}}在解说乔纳斯和约瑟夫的2018年[[經典俄羅斯方塊世界錦標賽|經典俄羅斯方塊世界錦標賽]]决赛时，戏谑地宣称乔纳斯是一个生活在西班牙[[阿尔瓦塞特|阿尔瓦塞特]]的60岁男子，而约瑟夫是一个来自[[卢森堡|卢森堡]]的16岁[[堡垒之夜|堡垒之夜]]玩家，诸多[[西语|西语]]媒体信以为真<ref>{{cite web |url=https://tetrisinterest.com/tetris-champion/ |website=Tetris Internet |accessdate=2021-01-10 |title=How did Jonas end up visiting Albacete, Spain? |archive-date=2021-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211019082936/https://tetrisinterest.com/tetris-champion/ }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author1=Comunidad Puyo Puyo Tetris Latam |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aLzaVBrTkIA |website=Youtube|title=Jonas, el español de 60 años oriundo de Albacete}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author1=Jonas Neubauer |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GG8LvYfUvok&t=404s |website=Youtube|title=Jonas Watches the CTWC, Part 5: Viva Albacete}}</ref>。乔纳斯因此受邀前往[[阿尔瓦塞特|阿尔瓦塞特]]，由市长亲授“城市之刀”并成为该城大使<ref>{{cite web |author1=Jonas Neubauer |url=https://twitter.com/neubsauce/status/1114664294908596224?s=20 |website=Twitter|title=I got a knife from the mayor and a wooden piece of art from a fan. Te amo y buenas noches, Albacete}}</ref>。2020年乔纳斯以假名西班牙人“BunBun”回归线上举办的[[经典俄罗斯方块世界锦标赛|经典俄罗斯方块世界锦标赛]]<ref>{{cite web |author1=eowobble |title=Seven-Time Classic Tetris World Champion, Jonas Neubauer |url=https://eowobble.com/2020/11/02/seven-time-classic-tetris-world-champion-jonas-neubauer/ |website=eowobble |accessdate=2021-01-18 |archive-date=2021-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210418134548/https://eowobble.com/2020/11/02/seven-time-classic-tetris-world-champion-jonas-neubauer/ }}</ref>。

